<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <%- include('partials/styles') %>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">ACCOUNT<span>GUARDIAN</span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="badge badge-alert">⚠ REFUND RATE ALERT</div>
    <h1><%= merchantName %>, your refund rate hit <%= (signalValue * 100).toFixed(2) %>%.</h1>
    <p class="subhead"><%= dateStr %> · Account Guardian monitoring</p>

    <p>Your refund rate has crossed our warning threshold of <span class="highlight"><%= (threshold * 100).toFixed(2) %>%</span>. A sustained elevated refund rate can trigger a Stripe account review — even without active disputes.</p>

    <div class="value-row">
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="label">CURRENT REFUND RATE</div>
        <div class="value signal-value-danger"><%= (signalValue * 100).toFixed(2) %>%</div>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="label">THRESHOLD</div>
        <div class="value signal-threshold"><%= (threshold * 100).toFixed(2) %>%</div>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card">
        <div class="label">OVER BY</div>
        <div class="value signal-value-danger">+<%= ((signalValue - threshold) * 100).toFixed(2) %>%</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="action-box action-box-warning">
      <h2>Recommended: Investigate refund patterns</h2>
      <p>A high refund rate often signals product dissatisfaction, unclear pricing, or fulfillment issues. Review your refund reasons in the Stripe dashboard — if the same SKU keeps getting refunded, start there. If refunds are tied to shipping delays, update your delivery estimates. Consider tightening your refund policy if abuse is a factor, but keep it compliant with your processor's requirements.</p>
    </div>

    <p>For a full remediation guide, visit: <a href="<%= appUrl %>/guides/high-refund-rate" class="guide-link"><%= appUrl %>/guides/high-refund-rate</a></p>

    <a href="<%= dashboardUrl %>" class="cta">View Your Dashboard →</a>

    <div class="footer">
      Account Guardian by Astramedia · Monitoring Stripe accounts so you don't get surprised<br>
      Questions? Reply to this email.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
